 02:12:11','',0,'http://www.accidentreview.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/expert-image1.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(1015,3,'2013-04-16 16:16:39','2013-04-16 16:16:39','<div align=\"center\"><img src=\"/wp-content/themes/accident-review/images/ar_graphic.png\" /></div>\r\n','Home','','publish','open','closed','','home','','','2013-06-04 21:54:54','2013-06-04 21:54:54','',0,'http://www.accidentreview.com/?page_id=1015',0,'page','',0),(1016,3,'2013-04-16 16:09:10','2013-04-16 16:09:10','<p>dev homepage</p>\n','Home (DEV)','','inherit','open','open','','1015-revision','','','2013-04-16 16:09:10','2013-04-16 16:09:10','',1015,'http://www.accidentreview.com/2013/04/1015-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(1017,3,'2013-04-16 16:16:39','2013-04-16 16:16:39','<p>dev homepage</p>\r\n','Home (DEV)','','inherit','open','open','','1015-revision-2','','','2013-04-16 16:16:39','2013-04-16 16:16:39','',1015,'http://www.accidentreview.com/2013/04/1015-revision-2/',0,'revision','',0),(1178,3,'2013-05-01 19:58:32','2013-05-01 19:58:32','<p>[agent-login-form type=login]</p>\r\n','Login','','inherit','open','open','','1034-revision-4','','','2013-05-01 19:58:32','2013-05-01 19:58:32','',1034,'http://www.accidentreview.com/2013/05/1034-revision-4/',0,'revision','',0),(1020,3,'2013-04-16 16:30:56','2013-04-16 16:30:56','<p>dev homepage</p>\r\n','Home (DEV)','','inherit','open','open','','1015-revision-3','','','2013-04-16 16:30:56','2013-04-16 16:30:56','',1015,'http://www.accidentreview.com/2013/04/1015-revision-3/',0,'revision','',0),(1021,3,'2013-04-16 20:51:28','2013-04-16 20:51:28','<h3>Fast, accurate assessments from industry experts at a fraction of the cost.</h3>\r\n<p>S. D. Lyons serves New England and eastern New York, delivering expert automotive forensic analysis and expert court testimony in several specialty areas, including:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Vehicle Accident Claims</li>\r\n	<li>Mechanical/Electrical Claims</li>\r\n	<li>Vehicle Theft Claims</li>\r\n	<li>Vehicle Fire Claims</li>\r\n	<li>Physical Damage Claims</li>\r\n	<li>Report Review Claims</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Our qualified experts perform not only comprehensive vehicle examinations, but also exhaustive research, incident scene inspections, and review of background information to ensure a thorough and impartial analysis. Our support staff provides our Engineers and Technicians with the resources and data they require, while offering prompt response to technical and other inquiries posed by our clients. With the capability for paperless invoicing and reporting, we&rsquo;ll deliver your results in the timeliest manner possible. Additionally, S. D. Lyons can provide, at no charge, seminars pertaining to any of our specialty areas.</p>\r\n','Services','','publish','open','open','','services','','','2013-04-16 21:59:36','2013-04-16 21:59:36','',1015,'http://www.accidentreview.com/?page_id=1021',0,'page','',0),(1022,3,'2013-04-16 20:51:16','2013-04-16 20:51:16','','Services','','inherit','open','open','','1021-revision','','','2013-04-16 20:51:16','2013-04-16 20:51:16','',1021,'http://www.accidentreview.com/2013/04/1021-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(1023,3,'2013-04-16 20:51:55','2013-04-16 20:51:55','<p>For over 20 years, the automotive forensic specialists at Acciden Review have provided insurance companies with the court-qualified, expert opinions they need to ensure their claims decisions are both credible and cost-effective.</p>\r\n<p>Experienced and unbiased, our automotive specialists have investigated thousands of motor vehicle accidents, testified as expert witnesses at numerous criminal and civil trials, and hold nationally-recognized accreditations and certifications.</p>\r\n<p>Offering nationwide consultative services, Accident Review specializes in Vehicle Theft Analysis, Mechanical Failure Analysis, Vehicle Fire Analysis, and Vehicle Accident Reconstruction. From automobiles, trucks and RVs to motorcycles, boats, and more, Accident Review can handle any type of motor vehicle or equipment &ndash; and provide a detailed, thorough judgment on the true cause of each and every insurance claim.</p>\r\n<h3>Mission</h3>\r\n<p>Accident Review has one mission: to provide fast, accurate, and cost-effective insurance claim assessments. With exemplary credentials and years of combined related service in the automotive and engineering fields, our entire staff is fully committed to providing insurance companies with the expert opinions they need &hellip; at a fraction of the time and cost.</p>\r\n<h3>Vision</h3>\r\n<p>Accident Review&rsquo;s vision is to deliver innovative, online claims decision solutions to insurance companies across the nation. To do this, Accident Review embraces the very latest in new technologies and industry developments, including high-tech accident scene mapping equipment, accident reconstruction software, and crash data retrieval capabilities.</p>\r\n<h3>Values</h3>\r\n<p>Nothing matters more than getting to the truth. Valuing impartiality and integrity above all else, we hold ourselves to the highest standards, ensuring the utmost in professionalism throughout all of our investigations.</p>\r\n','About Us','','publish','open','open','','about-us','','','2013-04-16 22:03:56','2013-04-16 22:03:56','',1015,'http://www.accidentreview.com/?page_id=1023',0,'page','',0),(1024,3,'2013-04-16 20:51:36','2013-04-16 20:51:36','','About Us','','inherit','open','open','','1023-revision','','','2013-04-16 20:51:36','2013-04-16 20:51:36','',1023,'http://www.accidentreview.com/2013/04/1023-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(1025,3,'2013-04-16 20:52:46','2013-04-16 20:52:46','<h3>Seamless, sophisticated solutions for today&#39;s automotive insurance industry.</h3>\r\n<h4>Safe, secure, and speedy claim reviews.</h4>\r\n<p>With AccidentReview.com&#39;s safe and secure online portal, insurance claim agents can obtain accurate, expert opinions within 24 hours &hellip; all at a low flat rate of $200.</p>\r\n<p>Available only to insurance companies, AccidentReview.com&#39;s exclusive online system provides the perfect solution for claims agents that need a fast yet accurate forensic assessment.</p>\r\n<p>Registered users will have access to a host of online claims management features, including claims tracking, access to your assigned claim representative, and more. Once your case is submitted, our automotive forensic experts will examine the data, documents, photographs, and any other pertinent information provided, and render an opinion within one business day.</p>\r\n<h4>Prompt and professional customer support.</h4>\r\n<p>Every single member of AccidentReview.com&#39;s staff is fully committed to providing our clients with the prompt and professional customer support they need to arrive at an accurate, cost-effective claim decision.</p>\r\n<p>Our highly-qualified experts perform comprehensive vehicle examinations, exhaustive research, incident scene inspections, and review of background information to ensure a thorough and impartial analysis on each claim review.</p>\r\n<p>Supporting our accredited Accident Reconstructionists and Automotive Forensic Technicians is our highly-trained office staff. They provide the research, analysis, and technical expertise that enables our Technicians and Engineers to expediently conduct their analyses and ensure the most accurate reports are delivered in a timely fashion.</p>\r\n','Customer Support','','publish','open','open','','customer-support','','','2013-04-16 22:06:28','2013-04-16 22:06:28','',1015,'http://www.accidentreview.com/?page_id=1025',0,'page','',0),(1026,3,'2013-04-16 20:52:12','2013-04-16 20:52:12','','Customer Support','','inherit','open','open','','1025-revision','','','2013-04-16 20:52:12','2013-04-16 20:52:12','',1025,'http://www.accidentreview.com/2013/04/1025-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(1027,3,'2013-04-16 20:51:55','2013-04-16 20:51:55','<p>{about us content}</p>\r\n','About Us','','inherit','open','open','','1023-revision-2','','','2013-04-